    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. You really have to see it to believe it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home!",
