    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint protected by a professional ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely free of chips, swirls, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats are supple with no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage. Every feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous, full-service history with all maintenance performed at the dealership. Always garaged and never driven in inclement weather, this car comes complete with both original keys, all factory manuals, and a folder of service records. It represents the pinnacle of its model\u2019s preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are privileged to present this peerless motorcar, maintained to the most exacting standards and preserved in impeccable, showroom condition. This vehicle represents a rare convergence of aesthetic perfection and mechanical integrity, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every component has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for excellence. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of the superlative, this specimen offers an unparalleled driving experience. We invite you to inspect this distinguished vehicle and appreciate its pristine state firsthand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
