    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, so it's in absolutely stunning shape inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
