    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 996.2 Carrera in concours-level condition. The M96/03 flat-six power plant is in peak mechanical health, featuring a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced rear main seal (RMS). The G96 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise, bolt-action engagement paired with a fresh Sachs clutch. This example boasts the factory M030 sport suspension package and pristine undercarriage integrity, still retaining original factory cosmoline. Zero evidence of bore scoring or chain guide wear; it is a turn-key specimen for the purist collector seeking optimal throttle response and chassis feedback.",
